{"word":"G4448 - πυρόω - pyróō - poo-ro'-o - Burn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πυρόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>pyróō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>poo-ro'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Burn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வேகு, எரி, அக்கினியாயிரு, புடமிடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to burn with fire, to set on fire, to kindle"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4442 - πῦρ - pŷr - poor/4442\">G4442</a>; to <i>kindle</i>, that is, (passively) to <i>be ignited</i>, <i>glow</i> (literally), <i>be refined</i> (by implication), or (figuratively) to <i>be inflamed</i> (with anger, grief, lust): - burn, fiery, be on fire, try."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4442 - πῦρ - pŷr - poor/4442\">G4442</a>, <a href=\"#/G4443 - πυρά - pyrá - poo-rah'/4443\">G4443</a>, <a href=\"#/G4447 - πύρινος - pýrinos - poo'-ree-nos/4447\">G4447</a>, <a href=\"#/G4448 - πυρόω - pyróō - poo-ro'-o/4448\">G4448</a>, <a href=\"#/G4449 - πυῤῥάζω - pyrrházō - poor-hrad'-zo/4449\">G4449</a>, <a href=\"#/G4450 - πυῤῥός - pyrrhós - poor-hros'/4450\">G4450</a>, <a href=\"#/G4451 - πύρωσις - pýrōsis - poo'-ro-sis/4451\">G4451</a>"}]}